Copyright (c) 2026 mitsuru contributors

This project was inspired by the design philosophy of:

- miina-proxy (https://github.com/kakumiina/miina-proxy)
  by kakumiina (AI秘書ミーナとミツル)
  Telemetry-zero, dependency-zero approach to LLM CLI output compression.

- RTK / Rust Token Killer (https://github.com/rtk-ai/rtk)
  Original concept of compressing CLI command output before it reaches an LLM.

No source code from the above projects has been copied into mitsuru.
The implementations are independent. Only the design philosophy and
problem statements were referenced.

We thank the authors of both projects for their contributions to the
AI developer tooling ecosystem.
